#- Tigen, 2/27/15§0
§0
§0Technology Will increase life expectancy, §0
§0
§0Increased automation leads to less manual labor & less non-STEM skills§0

#- 
§0Technology advancement will lead to much more tension in society §0
§0
§0Sexual degeneration will become worse but more accepted
#- The oil market will be held by a string - extracting oil will go from safe and easy to difficult, dangerous, and innefficient
#- Oil market will be on the way out until a level replacement is found for energy sources - but with a fight from the existing tycoons.
#- Globalization & widespread unity will not halt due to world-wide dependence upon it.§0
§0A large war will break out in the Western world most likely between the West(Europe, America) and the East(Russia, China)§0

#- Suprabuilder§0
§0
§0The world powers have collapsed much to the like of Rome.§0
§0
§0Russia is a dystopian world power. They would not have conquered much past Poland due to in-fighting and reactionaries.
#- Europe will be similar to the early medieval days - hundreds of thousands of small kingdoms within former nations. §0
§0
§0These "kingdoms" will be self-dependant city-states. Cities with more history will be dominant and rule over the other cities.
#- These city-states will begin as locally ruled and small. Every city-state will have a different religion, government, and demographics to several degrees. §0
§0
§0Religion will be dominant once again, athiesm will fade as life gets hard again
#- Life expectancy will drop to 40 until the generations of the old world are gone. After that, it will slowly creep up until all humans have adapted to the new life. §0
§0
§0Science will go back to discovering new things with a bases of religion, used when useful
#- Racial diversity will be accepted for the first years, but the minorities will become discriminated as time goes on, and kicked out once a connected majority is established.§0
§0
§0SJW's, Jews and leftists will evacuate or be lynched
#- Media will be purged by the new society. We will eventually stop using electric media all together, or become obsessed again.§0
§0
§0New leaders will arise in time with uncanny talents, leading their nations to new heights as Charlemagne and Caesar had. 
#- America will become isolated from the rest of the world and rule inward. They will have 50% of their present power and prosperity, but dispersed to the government. §0
§0
§0Martial law, slums, poverty, underground societies and general dystopia will be America
#- Jesus will have His second coming at any time after the Fall of the West. Rapture at any time. §0
§0
§0Israel will be the center of World events and interest.§0
§0
§0The Middle East will be filled with Muslims and Jew-Muslim shills
#- This is /pol/'s opinions on the Post-Modern World. 

I hope you enjoyed our predictions. May none of them come true.

Bless Wulfkhaine. Amen.
